Cell["8. Boundary relation for the two solutions", "Section",ExpressionUUID->"1802e64b-4c4a-4c94-8841-457998ef5a24"],

Cell["\<\
This checks -2 I zeta'(0+) = lam^2 zeta(0+). Series is used instead of \
one-sided Limit to avoid Direction-option issues.\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"b3d0a883-44aa-4395-9170-a6b06f40e067"],

