Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Conclusion", "Section",ExpressionUUID->"29abe4e8-bdc6-4ac2-bac1-a13b428ff113"],

Cell["\<\
The essential certifications are: lapEquationCheck = 0, shiftCheck = 0, \
lPlusResidual = lMinusResidual = 0, transformBackPlus = transformBackMinus = \
0 if Mathematica can finish them, numerical ODE residuals equal zero after \
Chop, and boundaryCheck11 = boundaryCheck12 = 0. Together these confirm the \
procedure for the two known bounded solutions.\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"f89c9de7-3c8c-4dd3-8938-c88bcfd9d4b6"]
}, Open  ]]
}, Open  ]]
